body:
Hello! My name is Nubels and I am a 18-year-old high diamond adc player from germany. My English is very fluid and I don't mind if the language of the team is English or German. I have been on the amateur teams Hybrid eSports before but that was quite a while ago and I struggle to improve playing only solo queue. Playing on a team would motivate to become better at the game.
My peak ranks are Master in EUW and Challenger on the Russian server, currently I am Diamond 2 EUW.
Please contact me!
My twitter
https://twitter.com/nubelss
My op.ggs
http://euw.op.gg/summoner/userName=FSL+Nubels (FSL is not a team, it is a tag my friends and me use)
http://ru.op.gg/summoner/userName=Nubels
